| Logout cookie domain mismatch | Next.js proxy rewrote all cookies unconditionally | `app/api/.ory/[...path]/route.ts` — commit `1f8471e` |
| Email OTP not sending | `mfa_enabled` nested under `config` instead of top-level | `kratos.tf` methods.code — resolved |
| Kratos CrashLoopBackOff | Invalid config key `second_factor_url` | `kratos.tf` — commit `1e41b75` |
| CORS preflight failing | `OPTIONS` missing from Kratos CORS allowed_methods | `kratos.tf` — resolved |
| Courier not sending email | `smtps://port-465` instead of `smtp://port-587` | `terraform.tfvars` smtp_connection_uri — commit `0b705e5` |
